and get a new result. For a few hours (until my labmates looked at the notes), I was the only person in the entire history of humanity to know the results of this simulation. Moments like this are why I became a physicist, and I'm so unspeakably happy that I get to have them again!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/njfwtKV</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Tchya]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>My costume for work today</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/90Z4dIF</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IEHklrJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I tried my best with the spider web makeup.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2jBa3gw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h8nxduu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I got the dress glove cape and headpiece at Goodwill and then I attached the spider webs to the dress.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WZZDT2m.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Happy Halloween to all you ghouls and goblins.
