Last year I walked around and handed out my old extra pokemon cards to kids.  Found out about "Trick or Trade" card boosters.  Now I have a mini side puch for quick hand offs.  

My area was hit by Halene.  This year I figured this year to hand out more cards.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ONDGyJX.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>My hidden stash of stole-er I mean legit pokemon for those pesky trainers to get!

